Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:16.98,Eyecatch_an6,Eyecatch,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1)}{Ascendance of a\N Bookworm}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.85,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.73,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:22.61,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:24.49,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:25.99,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:27.48,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I don't want to!}Không muốn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:28.98,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Stop it!}Dừng lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:30.48,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.87,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Let go of Main!}Thả Myne ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:36.54,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Main, are you all right?}Con ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.05,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{You insolent peasant!}Tên khốn xấc xược!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:42.93,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Dad!}Ba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.95,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{This is... nothing...}Chẳng sao... cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.16,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Dad!}Ba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.36,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Dad! Dad!}Ba! Ba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.32,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{You won't get away with this.}Không thể tha thứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.10,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Count Bindewald!}Bá tước Bindewald!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:06.03,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Don't think the same trick will keep working!}Đừng nghĩ một trò làm được 2 lần!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:13.29,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{I'm not scared of you, child!}Ta không sợ ngươi đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:27.63,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{This is a magic stone of \Ndarkness that absorbs mana!}Đây là đá ma thuật bóng đêm có thể hút ma lực.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:34.03,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Futile! Absolutely futile!}Vô ích vô ích!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:42.43,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{What?}Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.71,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Wh-What's the meaning of this?}C-Cái gì thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:05.98,Default,High Priest,0,0,0,,{Main!}Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:09.21,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Just how much...}Ngươi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.15,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{I let my guard down...}Ta đã lơ là...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:22.61,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{To think she possessed this much mana.}Không ngờ nó lại nhiều ma lực đến thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.23,Default,Damuel,0,0,0,,{Apprentice Priestess!}Nữ tu tập sự!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:29.74,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Sir Damuel!}Ngài Damuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:34.00,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{How pathetic to call yourself a knight\N when you have so little mana.}Vậy mà cũng tự gọi là kị sĩ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.42,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Head Priest!}Ngài linh mục trưởng!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.48,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{What is the meaning of this?}Chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.37,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{What are you doing here?}Tại sao ngài lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:02.94,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{You should be away.}Đáng ra phải khuất mắt chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:07.43,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{I'd announced that I was away...}Tôi đã được thông báo đi khuất mắt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:12.94,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{But it appears as though a stranger \Nhas entered the cathedral.}Nhưng có một kẻ lạ mặt đã bước vào nhà thờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.44,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{High Priest, who is this?}Ai đây, ngài giáo hoàng?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:19.21,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{A noble from Ahrensbach!}Quý tộc vùng Ahrensbach!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:21.69,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{If you could kindly show me your permit.}Cho phép tôi xem giấy giới thiệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:25.21,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{Why must I show anything to a mere priest?}Tại sao ta phải cho ngươi xem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:27.65,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Well, since our lord is currently away,}Hiện tại ngài lãnh chúa đang vắng mặt,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:30.71,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{no noble from another domain \Nis allowed to enter this city.}không một quý tộc vùng khác nào có thể vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:33.97,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{Are you trying to suggest \Nthat I forged my permit?}Ý ngươi là ta giả mạo giấy phép?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:36.72,Default,High Priest,0,0,0,,{He has been granted proper permission.}Ông ấy đã được cho phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:40.54,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{We had established some \Nnew rules this winter.}Chúng tôi đã thiết lập một số quy tắc mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.57,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Were you not aware of them?}Ngài vẫn chưa biết sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:44.89,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{New rules?}Quy tắc mới?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.73,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Ah... Please forgive me.}A... xin thứ lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.94,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{The winter social is for nobles.}Mùa đông dành cho giới quý tộc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:54.00,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Of course, you wouldn't know.}Dĩ nhiên ngài không biết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:58.31,Default,High Priest,0,0,0,,{M-More importantly, do something about Main!}Q-Quan trọng hơn làm gì đó với nó đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:00.49,Default,High Priest,0,0,0,,{I'm not the one who caused all this trouble!}Ta không phải kẻ gây ra chuyện này!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:01.76,Default,High Priest,0,0,0,,{It was Main!}Là Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:02.63,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{What?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:06.21,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{I was viciously attacked.}Ta đã bị tấn công.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:09.37,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{She had the nerve to attack \Nme, a noble, with her mana.}Nó dùng ma lực tấn công lên ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:13.26,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Capture Main for committing \Ntreason against a noble!}Tử hình Myne vì đã tấn công quý tộc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.94,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Main, you let your mana go berserk again?}Myne, con lại để ma lực mất kiểm soát?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:18.93,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{It was an emergency.}Là tình huống khẩn cấp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.25,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{I can see that.}Ta biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:25.77,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Head Priest... am I going \Nto be charged with a crime?}Linh mục trưởng... con sẽ bị bắt sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.69,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:30.22,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Because we are dealing with the high \Npriest and a noble from another domain.}Vì đối phương là giáo hoàng và quý tộc vùng khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:36.40,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Not just yourself, but your family and \Nyour attendants will all be charged.}Không chỉ con, gia đình, học việc, tất cả sẽ bị tử hình.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.84,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, Dad.}Con xin lỗi ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:42.71,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{I was prepared to die as soon as \Nyou started going to the cathedral.}Ba đã chuẩn bị tinh thần từ khi con vào nhà thờ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.27,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{This is no different.}Lần này cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:55.13,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Lord Sylvester, you liar.}Ngày Sylvester nói dối.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:57.55,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{You promised to protect me.}Đã hứa sẽ bảo vệ mình rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:00.81,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Main, where did you get that?}Myne, con có nó ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:03.59,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{He gave it to me after he went hunting.}Ngài ấy đưa lúc bọn con đi săn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:05.42,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{He said it was a protective charm.}Nói đây là bùa hộ mệnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.18,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{I see.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:11.93,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{That is a powerful protective charm indeed.}Đúng là bùa hộ mệnh mạnh mẽ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:13.81,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{What do you mean by that?}Ý cha là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:15.23,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{That's only...}Con...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:20.04,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{if you are prepared to become \NSylvester's daughter.}sẽ trở thành con gái của Sylvester.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:25.94,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{You mean Lord Sylvester \Ninstead of Lord Karstedt?}Ngài Sylvester chứ không phải ngài Karstedt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.04,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Correct.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.94,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{But not in two years.}Nhưng không chỉ trong 2 năm nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.46,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{This would be immediately.}Mà là ngay lúc này.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.36,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:38.54,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{If you have that resolve, you'll \Nbe able to save your family.}Nếu làm thế, con có thể cứu gia đình mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:49.72,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Absolutely not. You're not \Nleaving us immediately!}Đừng! Con không được làm thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.85,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{If that is how to save everyone...}Nếu đây là cách cứu mọi người...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.60,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Then I will proceed.}Vậy con sẽ làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.24,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Main!}Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.22,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I want to protect everyone.}Con muốn bảo vệ mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.00,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Please forgive me, Dad.}Hãy tha thứ cho con.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:18.23,Default,Gunther,0,0,0,,{Main...}Myne...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:25.43,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{If you've made up your mind...}Nếu đã chuẩn bị tinh thần rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:28.67,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Main, pray to the wind and protect them.}Myne, cầu chúc và bảo vệ họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:32.51,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Protect them from my mana.}Bảo vệ họ khỏi ma lực của ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.32,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{From your mana?}Của linh mục trưởng?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:40.13,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{We've just received this justification.}Mãi mới có được cơ hội này.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.77,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{I will now take this moment to be \Nrid of those who stand in my way.}Ta sẽ không để kẻ nào cản trở đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:47.23,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Head Priest, have you \Nsealed away Main's mana?}Linh mục trưởng, đã phong ấn ma lực của Myne chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:50.58,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Let Count Bindewald dispose of that vermin.}Hãy để bá tước Bindewald xử lý con nhãi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:53.48,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{It's best to throw her out of this domain.}Ném nó ra khỏi vùng cai trị này.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:59.12,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{What do you think you're doing?}Ngươi làm gì thế hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:02.01,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Wh-What are you doing?!}T-Thế này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.52,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{You dying right now will \Njust cause me issues later.}Ngài chết lúc này sẽ rất phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:10.39,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{What?! Quit fooling around and untie me!}Hả? Đừng có đùa nữa. Mau thả ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:13.80,Default,High priest,0,0,0,,{Are you defying my orders?!}Ngươi chống lệnh à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:17.32,Default,Bindewald,0,0,0,,{Why does a priest have a schtappe?}Tại sao linh mục trưởng lại có đũa phép?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:23.79,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Why... it's because I am a noble who \Ngraduated from the Royal Academy, of course,}Đó là vì... tôi cũng là một quý tộc\N tốt nghiệp từ học viện hoàng gia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:25.32,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Count Bindewald.}Bá tước Bindewald.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:31.00,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{You may think it's safe for \Nyou once you leave Ehrenfest,}Có thể ông nghĩ rằng sẽ an toàn khi rời khỏi Ehrenfest,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:35.43,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{but don't think for a second \NI'm letting you escape.}nhưng đừng nghĩ rằng ta cho phép điều đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:48.74,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Goddess of Wind that rules \Nover protection, Schutzaria,}Nữ thần gió bảo hộ, Schutzaria,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:52.92,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{and the twelve kindred \Ngoddesses at her side...}và 12 nữ thần phụng sự...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:58.36,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Hear my prayer and grant me holy power!}Xin hãy nghe lời cầu nguyện và cho con sức mạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:03.36,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Grant me a shield of wind that will \Nward away those who wish to do us harm!}Hãy ban cho chúng con lá chắn\N bảo vệ khỏi những kẻ muốn xâm hại!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:21.56,Italics,Main,0,0,0,,{Everyone here... My family...}Mọi người... gia đình mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:23.29,Italics,Main,0,0,0,,{I'm going to protect them!}Mình sẽ bảo vệ họ!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:22:59.94,Next_Chapter,Sign,0,0,0,,{Next Chapter\NBlessing}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:03.89,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Jeez, you should've saved \Nus earlier, Head Priest.}Sao không đến sớm hơn vậy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.89,0:23:06.25,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{I didn't know what was going on. \NThere's no helping that.}Ta còn chưa biết chuyện gì xảy ra nên chịu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.25,0:23:08.89,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Well, since you came out of your quarters,}Cha từ trong phòng đi ra,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:10.92,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{you must have been in your secret room.}hẳn là trốn trong phòng bí mật nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:15.32,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Correct. I was doing some research \Nregarding this current incident.}Phải, ta đang tìm kiếm thông tin cho việc lần này.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.32,0:23:20.67,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Sir Damuel mentioned he used\N ordonnanz, but you didn't reply.}Ngài Damuel đã sử dụng báo hiệu mà cha không trả lời.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.67,0:23:23.51,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Ordonnanz doesn't reach my hidden room.}Nó không thể ảnh hưởng đến phòng bí mật.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:25.90,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Then how did you find out what was going on?}Vậy sao cha biết chuyện?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:30.54,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Zahm had delivered a magic message\Nfrom the knight at the north gate to me.}Zahm đã đưa ta tin nhắn ma thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.54,0:23:34.66,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I see... Wait, what's a magic message?}Vậy à? Khoan, tin nhắn ma thuật là gì?
